This plugin bundles unmodified template and catalog assets from the
eGovFramework/egovframe-vscode-initializr project
(https://github.com/eGovFramework/egovframe-vscode-initializr),
pinned to the official v5.0.6 tag and licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
The corresponding upstream source checkout is tracked as a Git submodule in the plugin source repository.

Bundled upstream assets:
  - templates/templates-projects.json, templates/templates-context-xml.json
  - templates/code/*.hbs (11 files)
  - templates/config/**/*.hbs (52 files)
  - templates/projects/pom/*.xml (18 files)
  - templates/projects/examples/egovframe-boot-web.zip,
    templates/projects/examples/egovframe-boot-simple-backend.zip
  (remaining example ZIPs are downloaded on demand from the same version tag
   and verified against pinned SHA-256 checksums)

This plugin also uses Handlebars.java (com.github.jknack:handlebars),
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
